# Highlight Selection – BMAD Approach

This project implements the same highlight selection feature using a **BMAD (agent-driven AI workflow)** approach.

The implementation was produced through an iterative AI-assisted workflow.

This repository is part of the Generative AI Evangelist assignment.

## Scoring Rules

Base scores

- goal = 4
- assist = 3
- card = 1

Preference boosts

- favorite player +8
- favorite team +5

## Architecture

Events Input  
↓  
Scoring Engine  
↓  
Filtering  
↓  
Sorting  
↓  
Highlights Output  

## Run

python src/highlight_selector.py

